', 'https://cdn2.jomashop.com/media/catalog/product/cache/bb8fda0b339dbe7c4b0b03f372ea5c01/t/i/tissot-prx-quartz-ice-blue-ladies-watch-t1370101135100.jpg']::text[], 'https://www.jomashop.com/tissot-prx-quartz-ice-blue-ladies-watch-t1370101135100.html', 249.38, 345.99, 'Combínalo con blazer crema, pantalón recto, pumps nude y perfume floral limpio para un conjunto pulido.', 'https://i.pinimg.com/736x/0e/f0/b8/0ef0b8d68a3710f2552bdd114aa5e043.jpg', ARRAY['mp-d04ffafba9a6', 'mp-f9f99f3e6118', 'mp-907d601e36bb']::text[], 'Para una ocasión elegante, este trío equilibra delicadeza y presencia: el midi fluye con el reloj de carátula azul, las pumps alargan la silueta y el tono perla mantiene un lujo sereno, perfecto para almuerzo formal o cóctel de temporada.', 'elegante', NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET name=EXCLUDED.name, brand=EXCLUDED.brand, type=EXCLUDED.type, gender=EXCLUDED.gender, description=EXCLUDED.description, image_url=EXCLUDED.image_url, images=EXCLUDED.images, source_url=EXCLUDED.source_url, base_price_usd=EXCLUDED.base_price_usd, final_price_usd=EXCLUDED.final_price_usd, styling_note=EXCLUDED.styling_note, inspiration_image=EXCLUDED.inspiration_image, reco_ids=EXCLUDED.reco_ids, reco_note=EXCLUDED.reco_note, reco_context=EXCLUDED.reco_context, reco_ids_w=EXCLUDED.reco_ids_w, reco_note_w=EXCLUDED.reco_note_w, reco_context_w=EXCLUDED.reco_context_w;
INSERT INTO products(id, source, source_id, name, brand, type, gender, description, image_url, images, source_url, base_price_usd, final_price_usd, styling_note, inspiration_image, reco_ids, reco_note, reco_context, reco_ids_w, reco_note_w, reco_context_w) VALUES ('mp-6bad761b5fb0', 'jomashop', 'SE-SRPG31K1', 'Seiko 5 Sports Automatic Grey Dial Men''s Watch', 'Seiko', 'watch', 'men', 'Esfera gris y líneas deportivas, una pieza versátil con carácter moderno y sobrio.', 'https://cdn2.jomashop.com/media/catalog/product/cache/bb8fda0b339dbe7c4b0b03f372ea5c01/s/e/seiko-5-sports-automatic-grey-dial-mens-watch-srpg31k1.jpg', ARRAY['https://cdn2.jomashop.com/media/catalog/product/cache/bb8fda0b339dbe7c4b0b03f372ea5c01/s/e/seiko-5-sports-automatic-grey-dial-mens-watch-srpg31k1.jpg', 'https://cdn2.jomashop.com/media/catalog/product/cache/bb8fda0b339dbe7c4b0b03f372ea5c01/s/e/seiko-5-sports-automatic-grey-dial-mens-watch-srpg31k1_2.jpg', 'https://cdn2.jomashop.com/media/catalog/product/cache/bb8fda0b339dbe7c4b0b03f372ea5c01/s/e/seiko-5-sports-automatic-grey-dial-mens-watch-srpg31k1_3.jpg', 'https://cdnstatic.creationwatches.com/products/product-images/l/SRPG31K1_LRG.webp', 'https://www.timewatches.co.za/cdn/shop/products/seiko-5-sports-field-grey-dial-automatic-mens-watch-srpg31k1-990161.jpg?v=1685730860&width=600', 'https://www.citywatches.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/SRPG31K1_3.jpg']::text[], 'https://www.jomashop.com/seiko-5-sports-automatic-grey-dial-mens-watch-srpg31k1.html', 249.99, 346.99, 'Úsalo con camisa oxford azul, chinos arena, loafers marrones y perfume amaderado suave.', 'https://myquickurl.com/cheerlives.com/43-cheerlives_gleamnest_20241122082932.webp', ARRAY['mp-c1386c461b8d', 'mp-e886cd56a6d2', 'mp-605a39d82c0f']::text[], 'Para ti, este look funciona con naturalidad: lino y algodón dan frescura, las sneakers aportan limpieza deportiva y el perfume añade un carácter aromático, ambarado y moderno. Ideal para fines de semana, viaje corto o verano en Lima.', 'casual', NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET name=EXCLUDED.name, brand=EXCLUDED.brand, type=EXCLUDED.type, gender=EXCLUDED.gender, description=EXCLUDED.description, image_url=EXCLUDED.image_url, images=EXCLUDED.images, source_url=EXCLUDED.source_url, base_price_usd=EXCLUDED.base_price_usd, final_price_usd=EXCLUDED.final_price_usd, styling_note=EXCLUDED.styling_note, inspiration_image=EXCLUDED.inspiration_image, reco_ids=EXCLUDED.reco_ids, reco_note=EXCLUDED.reco_note, reco_context=EXCLUDED.reco_context, reco_ids_w=EXCLUDED.reco_ids_w, reco_note_w=EXCLUDED.reco_note_w, reco_context_w=EXCLUDED.reco_context_w;
INSERT INTO products(id, source, source_id, name, brand, type, gender, description, image_url, images, source_url, base_price_usd, final_price_usd, styling_note, inspiration_image, reco_ids, reco_note, reco_context, reco_ids_w, reco_note_w, reco_context_w) VALUES ('mp-55ea6c1d6bbe', 'jomashop', 'Z-QV2QT', 'Gucci The Voice Of The Snake, Oud, Eau De Parfum 3.4 oz (100 ml)', 'Gucci', 'perfume', 'unisex', 'Oud profundo con estela intensa, pensado para una presencia sofisticada y magnética.', 'https://cdn2.jomashop.com/media/catalog/product/cache/bb8fda0b339dbe7c4b0b03f372ea5c01/g/u/gucci-the-voice-of-the-snake-oud-eau-de-parfum-34-oz-100-ml-3614227768031.jpg', ARRAY['https://cdn2.jomashop.com/media/catalog/product/cache/bb8fda0b339dbe7c4b0b03f372ea5c01/g/u/gucci-the-voice-of-the-snake-oud-eau-de-parfum-34-oz-100-ml-3614227768031.jpg', 'https://cdn2.jomashop.com/media/catalog/product/cache/bb8fda0b339dbe7c4b0b03f372ea5c01/g/u/gucci-the-voice-of-the-snake-oud-eau-de-parfum-34-oz-100-ml-3614227768031_2.jpg', 'https://www.fahsbeauty.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/3614227768031.jpg', 'https://d3e7ardzpaj3y4.cloudfront.net/image/catalog/product/1705580514_25382_85597075_3614227768031-1-1500x1500.png', 'https://d3e7ardzpaj3y4.cloudfront.net/image/catalog/product/1705580548_25382_3902877_3614227768031-2-1500x1500.png']::text[], 'https://www.jomashop.com/gucci-the-voice-of-the-snake-oud-eau-de-parfum-100-ml-3614227768031.html', 249.99, 346.99, 'Acompáñalo con sastrería negra, reloj metálico pulido y cuero oscuro para una presencia nocturna refinada.', 'https://storage.googleapis.com/windsor-cms/media/2023/10/8c9595cf-what-to-wear-to-a-black-tie-16-dresses-hero-1.jpg', ARRAY['mp-1e4d84f905c4', 'mp-3c75f66f94e0', 'mp-1f0254abf485']::text[], 'Para una noche refinada, la camisa satinada aporta brillo discreto, los loafers de terciopelo elevan el conjunto y el reloj añade un acento sobrio. El oud del perfume es profundo, cálido y elegante, ideal para cena o evento nocturno.', 'noche', ARRAY['mp-270a92a68fd4', 'mp-95ac9c8c22b8', 'mp-c798e1926e9d']::text[], 'Para una noche elegante, el vestido abraza la silueta con sobriedad, los pumps estilizan y el reloj suma un brillo refinado. El oud del perfume es oscuro, cálido y envolvente, perfecto para cena formal o gala.', 'noche') ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET name=EXCLUDED.name, brand=EXCLUDED.brand, type=EXCLUDED.type, gender=EXCLUDED.gender, description=EXCLUDED.description, image_url=EXCLUDED.image_url, images=EXCLUDED.images, source_url=EXCLUDED.source_url, base_price_usd=EXCLUDED.base_price_usd, final_price_usd=EXCLUDED.final_price_usd, styling_note=EXCLUDED.styling_note, inspiration_image=EXCLUDED.inspiration_image, reco_ids=EXCLUDED.reco_ids, reco_note=EXCLUDED.reco_note, reco_context=EXCLUDED.reco_context, reco_ids_w=EXCLUDED.reco_ids_w, reco_note_w=EXCLUDED.reco_note_w, reco_context_w=EXCLUDED.reco_context_w;
INSERT INTO products(id, source, source_id, name, brand, type, gender, description, image_url, images, source_url, base_price_usd, final_price_usd, styling_note, inspiration_image, reco_ids, reco_note, reco_context, reco_ids_w, reco_note_w, reco_context_w) VALUES ('mp-33c53e7b9d78', 'theoutnet', 'ton-46376663163074476', 'Knitted Midi Dress', 'Tom Ford', 'clothing', 'women', 'Vestido midi tejido con línea depurada, pensado para una presencia serena y precisa.', 'https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163074476/F/w1020_q80.jpg', ARRAY['https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163074476/F/w1020_q80.jpg', 'https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163074476/Q/w1020_q80.jpg', 'https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163074476/D/w1020_q80.jpg', 'https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163074476/E/w1020_q80.jpg', 'https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163074476/N/w1020_q80.jpg']::text[], 'https://www.theoutnet.com/en-us/shop/product/tom-ford/dresses/midi-dresses/knitted-midi-dress/46376663163074476', 250, 346.99, 'Acompáñalo con reloj joya discreto, perfume floral oscuro y sandalias negras de tiras finas.', 'https://mytrendboutique.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/0_0_640_N-2-229.webp', ARRAY['mp-f9f99f3e6118', 'mp-69e7777fc13e', 'mp-907d601e36bb']::text[], 'Para ti, el vestido se ve impecable con pumps delicadas y un reloj clásico; el conjunto es sofisticado sin exceso. El perfume aporta un oud cremoso y resinoso, ideal para cena, cóctel o una noche especial.', 'noche', NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET name=EXCLUDED.name, brand=EXCLUDED.brand, type=EXCLUDED.type, gender=EXCLUDED.gender, description=EXCLUDED.description, image_url=EXCLUDED.image_url, images=EXCLUDED.images, source_url=EXCLUDED.source_url, base_price_usd=EXCLUDED.base_price_usd, final_price_usd=EXCLUDED.final_price_usd, styling_note=EXCLUDED.styling_note, inspiration_image=EXCLUDED.inspiration_image, reco_ids=EXCLUDED.reco_ids, reco_note=EXCLUDED.reco_note, reco_context=EXCLUDED.reco_context, reco_ids_w=EXCLUDED.reco_ids_w, reco_note_w=EXCLUDED.reco_note_w, reco_context_w=EXCLUDED.reco_context_w;
INSERT INTO products(id, source, source_id, name, brand, type, gender, description, image_url, images, source_url, base_price_usd, final_price_usd, styling_note, inspiration_image, reco_ids, reco_note, reco_context, reco_ids_w, reco_note_w, reco_context_w) VALUES ('mp-398be9443574', 'jomashop', 'Z-EQSFP', 'Yves Saint Laurent Unisex Blouse Impertinent Rose EDP Spray 4.2 oz', 'Yves Saint Laurent', 'perfume', 'unisex', 'Rosa impertinente con faceta limpia y moderna, elegante sin perder carácter.', 'https://cdn2.jomashop.com/media/catalog/product/cache/bb8fda0b339dbe7c4b0b03f372ea5c01/y/v/yves-saint-laurent-unisex-blouse-impertinent-rose-edp-spray-42-oz-fragrances-3614274184839.jpg', ARRAY['https://cdn2.jomashop.com/media/catalog/product/cache/bb8fda0b339dbe7c4b0b03f372ea5c01/y/v/yves-saint-laurent-unisex-blouse-impertinent-rose-edp-spray-42-oz-fragrances-3614274184839.jpg', 'https://nuochoamc.com/upload/images/san-pham/2876/yves-saint-laurent-blouse-edp2.webp', 'https://perfumedubai.com/cdn/shop/files/3614274184839-3_6acbe017-0635-4380-8203-a331da79891e.jpg?v=1757688524', 'https://www.yslbeauty.ca/dw/image/v2/AATL_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-ysl-master-catalog/default/dwb86fc46e/images/PACKSHOTS/FRAGRANCE/WW-51374YSL/3614274184839/3614274184839_blouse_edp_35ml_alt3.jpg?sw=768&sh=768&sm=cut&sfrm=jpg&q=85']::text[], 'https://www.jomashop.com/yves-saint-laurent-unisex-blouse-impertinent-rose-edp-spray-4-2-oz-fragrances-3614274184839.html', 250.79, 347.99, 'Combínalo con reloj dorado tenue, blusa cruda y pantalón negro recto con mules pulidos.', 'https://thefemmena.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/quiet-luxury-outfit-ideas-anoukyve.jpeg', ARRAY['mp-76e86cc39c9a', 'mp-a1a9c18f6ebe', 'mp-23af6e30e1cc']::text[], 'Para un hombre de gusto sobrio, este conjunto es impecable: el pantalón estructurado ordena, los loafers refinan y el reloj aporta presencia sin ruido. Perfecto para oficina creativa o cena; la pieza mecánica añade carácter atemporal.', 'lujo-silencioso', ARRAY['mp-86d959f332e4', 'mp-4f1a6a5f486b', 'mp-c798e1926e9d']::text[], 'Para una mujer que prefiere discreción refinada, el pantalón fluido, las flats y el reloj madreperla crean armonía limpia. El perfume, con rosa y matices aterciopelados, suma suavidad elegante; ideal para oficina, cena íntima o entretiempo.', 'lujo-silencioso') ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET name=EXCLUDED.name, brand=EXCLUDED.brand, type=EXCLUDED.type, gender=EXCLUDED.gender, description=EXCLUDED.description, image_url=EXCLUDED.image_url, images=EXCLUDED.images, source_url=EXCLUDED.source_url, base_price_usd=EXCLUDED.base_price_usd, final_price_usd=EXCLUDED.final_price_usd, styling_note=EXCLUDED.styling_note, inspiration_image=EXCLUDED.inspiration_image, reco_ids=EXCLUDED.reco_ids, reco_note=EXCLUDED.reco_note, reco_context=EXCLUDED.reco_context, reco_ids_w=EXCLUDED.reco_ids_w, reco_note_w=EXCLUDED.reco_note_w, reco_context_w=EXCLUDED.reco_context_w;
INSERT INTO products(id, source, source_id, name, brand, type, gender, description, image_url, images, source_url, base_price_usd, final_price_usd, styling_note, inspiration_image, reco_ids, reco_note, reco_context, reco_ids_w, reco_note_w, reco_context_w) VALUES ('mp-1957de84ee3b', 'theoutnet', 'ton-46376663163096266', 'French Cotton Terry Hoodie', 'Onia', 'clothing', 'men', 'Hoodie de terry francés con textura amable y silueta relajada.', 'https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163096266/F/w1020_q80.jpg', ARRAY['https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163096266/F/w1020_q80.jpg', 'https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163096266/R/w1020_q80.jpg', 'https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163096266/D/w1020_q80.jpg', 'https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163096266/E/w1020_q80.jpg', 'https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163096266/N/w1020_q80.jpg']::text[], 'https://www.theoutnet.com/en-us/shop/product/onia/tops/hoodies-zip-throughs/french-cotton-terry-hoodie/46376663163096266', 251, 347.99, 'Llévalo con reloj de acero, perfume limpio y joggers beige con sneakers blancas.', 'https://myquickurl.com/cheerlives.com/43-cheerlives_gleamnest_20241122082932.webp', ARRAY['mp-6abb16f437af', 'mp-bfd2adc26426', 'mp-2ecaf353c55e']::text[], 'Para ti, el hoodie se equilibra con shorts limpios, sneakers técnicas y un reloj de espíritu activo. La combinación es cómoda y pulida, ideal para fin de semana, aeropuerto o entrenamiento ligero con estilo.', 'deportivo', NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET name=EXCLUDED.name, brand=EXCLUDED.brand, type=EXCLUDED.type, gender=EXCLUDED.gender, description=EXCLUDED.description, image_url=EXCLUDED.image_url, images=EXCLUDED.images, source_url=EXCLUDED.source_url, base_price_usd=EXCLUDED.base_price_usd, final_price_usd=EXCLUDED.final_price_usd, styling_note=EXCLUDED.styling_note, inspiration_image=EXCLUDED.inspiration_image, reco_ids=EXCLUDED.reco_ids, reco_note=EXCLUDE