y deporte, el reloj de buceo se acompaña mejor de swim shorts limpios, sneakers ligeras y Gentleman Society Sport. La fragancia es fresca, limpia y energética; ideal para días de playa o paseo.', 'deportivo', NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET name=EXCLUDED.name, brand=EXCLUDED.brand, type=EXCLUDED.type, gender=EXCLUDED.gender, description=EXCLUDED.description, image_url=EXCLUDED.image_url, images=EXCLUDED.images, source_url=EXCLUDED.source_url, base_price_usd=EXCLUDED.base_price_usd, final_price_usd=EXCLUDED.final_price_usd, styling_note=EXCLUDED.styling_note, inspiration_image=EXCLUDED.inspiration_image, reco_ids=EXCLUDED.reco_ids, reco_note=EXCLUDED.reco_note, reco_context=EXCLUDED.reco_context, reco_ids_w=EXCLUDED.reco_ids_w, reco_note_w=EXCLUDED.reco_note_w, reco_context_w=EXCLUDED.reco_context_w;
INSERT INTO products(id, source, source_id, name, brand, type, gender, description, image_url, images, source_url, base_price_usd, final_price_usd, styling_note, inspiration_image, reco_ids, reco_note, reco_context, reco_ids_w, reco_note_w, reco_context_w) VALUES ('mp-b1fbf8bfa1e0', 'theoutnet', 'ton-46376663163096532', 'Tapered Lyocell Twill Pants', 'Onia', 'clothing', 'men', 'Pantalón tapered de lyocell, fluido y actual, ofrece una caída pulida con comodidad.', 'https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163096532/F/w1020_q80.jpg', ARRAY['https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163096532/F/w1020_q80.jpg', 'https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163096532/R/w1020_q80.jpg', 'https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163096532/D/w1020_q80.jpg', 'https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163096532/E/w1020_q80.jpg', 'https://www.theoutnet.com/variants/images/46376663163096532/N/w1020_q80.jpg']::text[], 'https://www.theoutnet.com/en-us/shop/product/onia/pants/casual-pants/tapered-lyocell-twill-pants/46376663163096532', 265, 364.99, 'Combínalo con reloj de acero, perfume amaderado y camisa oxford; completa con mocasines café.', 'https://thevou.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Business-Formal-Attire-Men.jpg', ARRAY['mp-69df0685227c', 'mp-2dc2d5978672', 'mp-7795ae7c1d60']::text[], 'Para oficina, estos pantalones funcionan con mocasines, reloj azul sobrio y Eau Sauvage. El conjunto es pulcro y versátil; perfecto para trabajo o almuerzos formales, con un perfume cítrico-aromático clásico y refinado.', 'oficina', NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET name=EXCLUDED.name, brand=EXCLUDED.brand, type=EXCLUDED.type, gender=EXCLUDED.gender, description=EXCLUDED.description, image_url=EXCLUDED.image_url, images=EXCLUDED.images, source_url=EXCLUDED.source_url, base_price_usd=EXCLUDED.base_price_usd, final_price_usd=EXCLUDED.final_price_usd, styling_note=EXCLUDED.styling_note, inspiration_image=EXCLUDED.inspiration_image, reco_ids=E