116_00.png?sm=fit&sw=1600&sh=1600', 'https://cdn2.jomashop.com/media/catalog/product/cache/bb8fda0b339dbe7c4b0b03f372ea5c01/t/i/tissot-seastar-quartz-diamond-white-mother-of-pearl-dial-unisex-watch-t1202101711600-t1202101711600_1.jpg']::text[], 'https://www.jomashop.com/tissot-seastar-quartz-diamond-white-mother-of-pearl-dial-unisex-watch-t120-210-17-116-00.html', 402.96, 534.99, 'Combínalo con blazer claro, pantalón recto y mocasines; perfume floral limpio y discreto.', 'https://www.chicstylecollective.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Belted-Bags-Trend.jpg', ARRAY['mp-4309d7661011', 'mp-08cb860e5a5a', 'mp-db86cdd766da']::text[], 'El reloj de madreperla se acompaña de un blazer estructurado y loafers pulidos, logrando un lujo sereno. Perfecto para oficina; el perfume aporta flores limpias, delicadas y luminosas.', 'oficina', NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET name=EXCLUDED.name, brand=EXCLUDED.brand, type=EXCLUDED.type, gender=EXCLUDED.gender, description=EXCLUDED.description, image_url=EXCLUDED.image_url, images=EXCLUDED.images, source_url=EXCLUDED.source_url, base_price_usd=EXCLUDED.base_price_usd, final_price_usd=EXCLUDED.final_price_usd, styling_note=EXCLUDED.styling_note, inspiration_image=EXCLUDED.inspiration_image, reco_ids=EXCLUDED.reco_ids, reco_note=EXCLUDED.reco_note, reco_context=EXCLUDED.reco_context, reco_ids_w=EXCLUDED.reco_ids_w, reco_note_w=EXCLUDED.reco_note_w, reco_context_w=EXCLUDED.reco_context_w;
